Arrête ça, Usopp !

00:10:11.140 --> 00:10:12.270
Il va te tuer.

00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:13.870
Boucle-la, toi !

00:10:14.190 --> 00:10:16.440
T'es à moitié mort, je te signale !

00:10:16.620 --> 00:10:17.780
